OL,3,CMan reunited with father's wartime
OL,4,Cdocuments found hidden in desk drawer
OL,6,FA man has told of his delight at being
OL,7,Freunited with Second World War
OL,8,Fdocuments that belonged to his father
OL,9,Fafter they were found hidden in a desk
OL,10,F18 years after he died.
OL,12,FMartin Reid bought the desk at auction
OL,13,Ffour years ago but only discovered the
OL,14,Ffolder of documents recently when he
OL,15,Fwas moving furniture and found them
OL,16,Fbehind a drawer that had been stuck.
