OL,3,CMan reunited with father's wartime
OL,4,Cdocuments found hidden in desk drawer
OL,6,FHe travelled from his home in Rye in
OL,7,FEast Sussex to meet Mr Reid in
OL,8,FEdinburgh on Thursday and to thank him
OL,9,Fpersonally as he collected the folder.
OL,11,FMr Rodger, 62, said he had a
OL,12,Fcollection of his father's old papers
OL,13,Fand letters from the war but had never
OL,14,Fseen the contents of the folder
OL,15,Fbefore, and he thanked Mr Reid for his
OL,16,F"kind return" of the documents.
