OL,3,CMan reunited with father's wartime
OL,4,Cdocuments found hidden in desk drawer
OL,6,FHe said: "In January 2021, with my 90-
OL,7,Fyear-old mother Isabel's health fast
OL,8,Fdeteriorating, I travelled from home
OL,9,Fin Sussex to Glasgow to help her move
OL,10,Finto a care home.
OL,12,F"Under lockdown rules this allowed
OL,13,Flittle time for preparation or even a
OL,14,Fproper goodbye, and then I was left
OL,15,Fwith less than two days to clear her
OL,16,Fflat, trying to preserve the memories
OL,17,Fof her own and my father's long and
OL,18,Frather remarkable lives.
