OL,3,CMan reunited with father's wartime
OL,4,Cdocuments found hidden in desk drawer
OL,6,FThe folder contained photographs,
OL,7,Fletters and maps relating to the
OL,8,FBritish Army's involvement in the
OL,9,Fcampaign known as the Liberation of
OL,10,FItaly between 1943 and 1945.
OL,12,FIan Rodger held the rank of captain
OL,13,Fduring the war and can be seen in a
OL,14,Fwartime photo which appears to feature
OL,15,FMajor Jack (John) Profumo ` who later
OL,16,Fbecame a secretary of state but whose
OL,17,Fpolitical career ended after an affair
OL,18,Fwith Christine Keeler came to light in
OL,19,Fthe 1960s.
