OL,3,CMan reunited with father's wartime
OL,4,Cdocuments found hidden in desk drawer
OL,6,FAfter being demobilised, Mr Rodger
OL,7,Fpractised as a solicitor in Glasgow,
OL,8,Fco-founded Scottish Opera and was
OL,9,Finvolved in the Scouts and Wellington
OL,10,FChurch of Scotland in Glasgow where he
OL,11,Fwas an elder.
OL,13,FHe died aged 91 in 2007 and in March
OL,14,F2021 his desk was put up for sale at
OL,15,FMcTear's Auctioneers in Glasgow. His
OL,16,Fwidow Isabel died in February 2023.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
