OL,6,FMr Reid, from Lanark in South
OL,7,FLanarkshire, bought it for #110 and
OL,8,Fused it regularly at his home over the
OL,9,Fyears, not knowing the historic papers
OL,10,Fwere hidden inside until he found them
OL,11,Fin late March this year.
