OL,3,CMan reunited with father's wartime
OL,4,Cdocuments found hidden in desk drawer
OL,6,F"This was a story that certainly
OL,7,Fcaptured the imagination of many
OL,8,Fpeople and Sandy got in touch with the
OL,9,Fchurch the morning the article was
OL,10,Fpublished, which was rather
OL,11,Fastonishing given he lives on the
OL,12,Fsouth coast of England," Mr Reid said.
OL,14,F"The maps, letters and photographs are
OL,15,Futterly fascinating and provide a
OL,16,Freally important insight into the
OL,17,FBritish Army's involvement in the
OL,18,FItalian campaign against Adolf
OL,19,FHitler's Germany.
